#, no-c-format
msgid "Select a &tex; group including the surrounding braces."
msgstr "एकं &tex; समूहः परितः ब्रेसिस् सहितम्।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1051
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,M</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Math Group</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,M</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>गणितसमूह</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1055
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select the current math group including the math commands."
msgstr "गणितस्य आदेशान् सहितं वर्तमानं गणितसमूहं चिनोतु ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1058
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,P</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Paragraph</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,P</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>अनुच्छेद</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1062
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select a whole paragraph, &ie; a group of text lines separated on both sides "
"by empty lines. A paragraph does not mean just continuous lines of text, as "
"it is in other text editors. This extended meaning also includes tables, "
"&latex; commands and all other lines of source. The only important thing for "
"&kile; is that this kind of paragraph is separated by two empty lines."
msgstr ""
"एकं सम्पूर्णं अनुच्छेदं चिनोतु, &ie; उभयतः शून्यरेखाभिः विभक्तः पाठरेखासमूहः । अनुच्छेदस्य अर्थः "
"केवलं निरन्तरपाठपङ्क्तयः एव न भवति, यथा अन्येषु पाठसम्पादकेषु भवति । अस्मिन् विस्तारिते अर्थे "
"सारणीः अपि अन्तर्भवन्ति, &latex; आदेशाः अन्याः सर्वाः स्रोतपङ्क्तयः च । एकमात्रं "
"महत्त्वपूर्णं वस्तु &kile; इति अस्ति यत् एतादृशः अनुच्छेदः शून्यरेखाद्वयेन विभक्तः भवति।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1070
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,L</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Line</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,L</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>रेखा</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1074
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select the text line of the current cursor position."
msgstr "वर्तमान कर्सरस्थानस्य पाठरेखां चिनोतु ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1078
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,W</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>TeX Word</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,W</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>TeX Word</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1082
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the word under the current cursor position. This selection has also "
"en extended meaning, because this command can also select &latex; commands, "
"which begin with a backslash and may also have an optional star at the end."
msgstr ""
"वर्तमान कर्सरस्थानस्य अधः शब्दं चिनोतु । अस्य चयनस्य en विस्तारितः अर्थः अपि अस्ति, यतः "
"एषः आदेशः &latex; आदेशाः, ये बैकस्लैश इत्यनेन आरभन्ते, अन्ते च वैकल्पिकं तारकं अपि भवितुम् "
"अर्हति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1093
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select &latex; commands"
msgstr "चयनं कुर्वन्तु &latex; आदेशाः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1095
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kile; has an extended feature to select &latex; commands. If you for "
"example have typed"
msgstr "&किले; &latex; आदेशाः । यदि भवान् उदाहरणार्थं टङ्कितवान् अस्ति"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:1098
#, no-c-format
msgid "text \\bfseries\\itshape more text"
msgstr "text \\bfseries\\itshape अधिक पाठ"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"and double click on one of the &latex; commands, both will be selected. But "
"often you only want to select one of two or more commands. This can be done "
"using the <keycombo>&Ctrl;</keycombo> key. You only have to press the "
"<keycombo>&Ctrl;</keycombo> key and a double click will only select the "
"desired command."
msgstr ""
"तथा &latex; आदेशान्, उभयम् अपि चयनं भविष्यति । परन्तु प्रायः भवन्तः केवलं द्वयोः वा "
"अधिकयोः आदेशयोः एकं चिन्वितुं इच्छन्ति । एतत् <keycombo>&Ctrl;</keycombo> कीलस्य "
"उपयोगेन कर्तुं शक्यते । भवद्भिः केवलं <keycombo>&Ctrl;</keycombo> कीलं नुदितव्यं तथा च "
"द्विवारं क्लिक् कृत्वा केवलं इष्टं आदेशं चिनोति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1111
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete"
msgstr "लुप्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To delete some parts of a document you can of course select them, and then "
"use the <keycombo><keycap>Delete</keycap></keycombo> key. &kate; also offers "
"the command <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>K</keycap></keycombo> which deletes the "
"whole line. But &kile; offers a faster way with its own delete commands. "
"Under <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guisubmenu>Delete</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice> you will find the following commands to delete text."
msgstr ""
"दस्तावेजस्य केचन भागाः विलोपयितुं भवान् अवश्यमेव तान् चिन्वतु, ततः "
"<keycombo><keycap>Delete</keycap></keycombo> कीलस्य उपयोगं कर्तुं शक्नोति । &कते; "
"<keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>K</keycap></keycombo> इति आदेशं अपि प्रदाति यत् सम्पूर्णां "
"रेखां विलोपयति । किन्तु &किले; स्वस्य delete आदेशैः सह द्रुततरं मार्गं प्रदाति । "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guisubmenu>Delete</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice> इत्यस्य अधः भवन्तः पाठं विलोपयितुं निम्नलिखित-आदेशान् प्राप्नुवन्ति ।"

#. Tag: screeninfo
