"keycombo> <keycap>,M</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>गणितसमूह</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1165
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete the current math group including the math commands."
msgstr "गणितस्य आदेशान् सहितं वर्तमानं गणितसमूहं विलोपयन्तु ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1168
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>T</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,P</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Paragraph</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>T</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,P</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>अनुच्छेद</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1172
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Delete a whole paragraph. Look at the <menuchoice><guisubmenu>Select</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Paragraph</guimenuitem></menuchoice> command, how a "
"paragraph is defined in &kile;."
msgstr ""
"एकं सम्पूर्णं अनुच्छेदं विलोपयन्तु। <menuchoice><guisubmenu>Select</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Paragraph</guimenuitem></menuchoice> आदेशं पश्यन्तु, "
"&kile;मध्ये अनुच्छेदः कथं परिभाषितः इति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1179
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>T</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,I</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>To End of Line</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>T</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,I</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>पङ्क्तिसमाप्त्यर्थं</"
"guimenuitem >"

#. Tag: para
